	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I used to have one of those adapters, but it broke down (Made in China TM power).<br />Since the cord was about 1CM long, it was not going to be reusable to I trashed it.<br /><br />I still have the earphones that shipped with it, but they tended to hurt my ears anyways (they are too big).

		

		</td>
